---
title: Quick Hot Honey Chicken Tacos with Buttery Cajun Potatoes and Cheddar Cheese
description: Mixing spicy hot sauce with sweet honey makes the perfect glaze for these Quick Hot Honey Chicken Tacos. Ready in less than 25 minutes, you'll also toss potatoes with a quick Cajun spiced butter.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R12_W42_UK_QR25532-4_Main_low-f0ca34e7.jpg
